 2312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van Gass, who was watched by wife Kathryn, said: \\\"I have got a fairly big friends and family group here.\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2433, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van Gass\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2337}, {\"ngram\": \"wife Kathryn\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2370}, {\"ngram\": \"a fairly big friends\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2410}, {\"ngram\": \"family group\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Seeing them here, their support, their love, their messages the last couple of days was incredible.\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2535, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their support\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2467}, {\"ngram\": \"their love\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2479}, {\"ngram\": \"their messages\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2495}, {\"ngram\": \"the last couple\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2511}, {\"ngram\": \"days\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It really carried me through quite a hard time \\\"I went into Tokyo as a bit of an underdog.\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2597, \"end\": 2602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999997805771513, \"rank\": 2.1928300089547745e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"quite a hard time\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2610}, {\"ngram\": \"an underdog\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To retain that title is a dream come true.\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2670, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that title\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2648}, {\"ngram\": \"a dream\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2659}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Fin is a phenomenal rider.\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2699, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fin\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2676}, {\"ngram\": \"a phenomenal rider\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Seeing him break that record just gave me a hunger in the belly to go harder.\\\"\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2778, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that record\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2728}, {\"ngram\": \"a hunger\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2750}, {\"ngram\": \"the belly\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Graham, who was also runner-up to Van Gass three years ago in Japan, said: \\\"It's a carbon copy to the Tokyo result.\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2895, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2780, \"end\": 2786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Graham\", \"score\": 0.9994157872345336, \"rank\": 0.0005126716980772453, \"text\": \"Graham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q188094\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Graham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Graham\"}, {\"begin\": 2842, \"end\": 2847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.7817797318245941, \"rank\": 0.18264568161485162, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 2882, \"end\": 2887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999997805771513, \"rank\": 2.1928300089547745e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"runner-up\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2810}, {\"ngram\": \"Van Gass\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2822}, {\"ngram\": \"a carbon copy\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This event is the strongest rider on the day wins and today that was Jaco \\\"Obviously it would have been nice to have had a bit of a different one, but this event is the strongest rider on the day wins and today that was Jaco.\", \"from\": 2897, \"to\": 3123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This event\", \"from\": 2897, \"to\": 2907}, {\"ngram\": \"the strongest rider\", \"from\": 2911, \"to\": 2930}, {\"ngram\": \"the day wins\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2946}, {\"ngram\": \"Jaco\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 2970}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 3018, \"to\": 3023}, {\"ngram\": \"a different one\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3042}, {\"ngram\": \"this event\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3058}, {\"ngram\": \"the strongest rider\", \"from\": 3062, \"to\": 3081}, {\"ngram\": \"the day wins\", \"from\": 3085, \"to\": 3097}, {\"ngram\": \"Jaco\", \"from\": 3117, \"to\": 3121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's shown that in the past and it's like, yeah, break a world record in qualifying and then have it for about five minutes before he takes it off me.\\\"\", \"from\": 3125, \"to\": 3277, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3153}, {\"ngram\": \"a world record\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3195}, {\"ngram\": \"qualifying\", \"from\": 3199, \"to\": 3209}, {\"ngram\": \"about five minutes\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jordan, who lost her eyesight after contracting a rare strain of E. coli bacteria as a university student, then topped the podium alongside pilot Danni Khan in the women's B 1000m time trial.\", \"from\": 3279, \"to\": 3470, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3279, \"end\": 3285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Grand_Prix\", \"score\": 0.9999999988726813, \"rank\": 1.0436327924724981e-09, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Grand_Prix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Grand_Prix\"}, {\"begin\": 3431, \"end\": 3435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shah_Rukh_Khan\", \"score\": 0.9999997932650544, \"rank\": 8.329837932311405e-08, \"text